maintext:
RALEIGH, N.C. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the North Carolina Lottery’s “Pick 4 Evening” game were:
0-8-7-7, Lucky Sum: 22
(zero, eight, seven, seven; Lucky Sum: twenty-two)
